WEBVTT

00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:38.240
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:41.270
[Episode 15]

00:01:44.590 --> 00:01:45.070
Sit.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:48.150
Sit.

00:01:49.870 --> 00:01:50.509
Sit!

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:52.150
Oh.

00:02:00.070 --> 00:02:01.670
What did I tell you back then?

00:02:02.170 --> 00:02:03.240
Repeat it to me.

00:02:05.310 --> 00:02:05.950
You...

00:02:07.150 --> 00:02:09.520
asked me to take good care of Lan.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.050
Exactly!

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:13.560
I did ask you to take good care of Lan,
didn't I?

00:02:13.870 --> 00:02:14.930
But what happened?

00:02:15.190 --> 00:02:15.630
Who...

00:02:15.870 --> 00:02:16.530
Who told you

00:02:16.590 --> 00:02:16.870
to

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:18.130
do that by kissing her?

00:02:18.870 --> 00:02:19.400
Besides,

00:02:20.020 --> 00:02:22.030
you knew your parents weren't home,

00:02:22.079 --> 00:02:23.310
but you still let Lan stay at your place.

00:02:23.310 --> 00:02:24.150
What were you up to?

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:25.590
What was on your mind?

00:02:31.030 --> 00:02:31.870
Mr. Yi,

00:02:33.070 --> 00:02:33.490
I...

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:36.110
I-I didn't know what I was thinking
either.

00:02:38.150 --> 00:02:39.710
I-I just like her.

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:41.910
I want to see her and spend time with her.

00:02:42.710 --> 00:02:44.160
So Xiaole

00:02:44.430 --> 00:02:46.590
actually likes you, Sister.

00:02:46.630 --> 00:02:48.150
What do you mean by "actually"?

00:02:48.150 --> 00:02:50.430
Many boys like your sister, alright?

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:52.590
How old are the two of you?

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:55.150
Do you even know what "like" means?

00:02:56.150 --> 00:02:56.630
Tell me

00:02:56.910 --> 00:02:57.710
what you think

00:02:57.870 --> 00:02:59.270
it means to like someone.

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:01.910
Li...

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:03.520
Liking...

00:03:06.470 --> 00:03:06.960
Li...

00:03:07.190 --> 00:03:07.800
Liking...

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:09.590
Li...

00:03:09.590 --> 00:03:09.870
Li...

00:03:09.870 --> 00:03:10.310
Liking someone

00:03:10.310 --> 00:03:13.110
just comes with the desire to spend time
together.

00:03:13.310 --> 00:03:14.630
Don't you dare smirk like that!

00:03:14.630 --> 00:03:15.760
Wipe that smirk off!

00:03:16.630 --> 00:03:17.630
Lan, I have to go now!

00:03:17.630 --> 00:03:18.690
How dare you laugh?

00:03:50.910 --> 00:03:52.640
Why didn't you answer my calls?

00:03:55.150 --> 00:03:56.210
My phone was taken.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:57.280
Taken?

00:03:57.310 --> 00:03:58.150
Shh.

00:04:11.870 --> 00:04:12.710
No way.

00:04:50.159 --> 00:04:50.750
Dad.

00:04:56.200 --> 00:04:56.510
Dad.

00:05:01.330 --> 00:05:02.530
I overslept, you see.

00:05:03.630 --> 00:05:05.830
-I'm hungry.
-I'll make you breakfast.

00:05:15.310 --> 00:05:16.160
Uncle Dong,

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:19.480
I'm here to drop off Lan's luggage
and cello case.

00:05:25.220 --> 00:05:26.750
Uncle Dong, I'm also here to apologize.

00:05:26.750 --> 00:05:27.770
I did wrong yesterday.

00:05:27.770 --> 00:05:28.510
I'm sorry.

00:05:28.870 --> 00:05:30.530
I prepared breakfast for you.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:31.720
I'll do anything

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:33.180
to earn your forgiveness.

00:05:33.270 --> 00:05:33.770
Breakfast!

00:05:33.770 --> 00:05:34.570
I'd love some.

00:06:02.270 --> 00:06:03.130
It tastes good.

00:06:10.270 --> 00:06:12.130
Xiaole seems like a nice guy to me.

00:06:12.430 --> 00:06:14.360
It's normal for Lan to date someone

00:06:14.520 --> 00:06:15.120
at her age.

00:06:15.870 --> 00:06:16.390
Dad,

00:06:16.950 --> 00:06:18.750
Xiaole is amazing.

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:21.270
Now I get to brag about

00:06:21.390 --> 00:06:23.750
his relationship with Sister at school.

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:26.070
Focus on eating, okay?

00:06:28.120 --> 00:06:29.720
Isn't Lan just a little girl?

00:06:29.790 --> 00:06:31.320
How can she date anyone now?

00:06:31.830 --> 00:06:33.370
It can wait till she turns 25.

00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:36.159
I had already been born when you were 25.

00:06:38.130 --> 00:06:38.690
You...

00:06:45.070 --> 00:06:45.750
Off to a ball game?

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:46.750
Will you go or not?

00:06:50.630 --> 00:06:51.190
You're playing chess.

00:06:51.190 --> 00:06:52.450
A critical point it is.

00:06:52.870 --> 00:06:54.040
You went grocery shopping?

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:55.720
Shopping for food, weren't you?

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:56.430
Yes, just some groceries.

00:06:56.430 --> 00:06:57.270
Care to join us?

00:06:57.270 --> 00:06:58.190
Sure, a moment later.

00:06:58.190 --> 00:06:58.600
Well,

00:06:58.630 --> 00:07:00.290
you're not that good a player.

00:07:01.430 --> 00:07:02.040
Glad that you know.

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:02.700
Uncle Dong.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.630
Why did you shop for groceries yourself?

00:07:04.630 --> 00:07:06.890
Let me run chores like this in the future.

00:07:06.910 --> 00:07:07.510
By the way,

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.830
you've been working your tail off lately.

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:11.760
Take this. It provides nutrition.

00:07:12.810 --> 00:07:15.700
[Bird's Nest]

00:07:16.630 --> 00:07:17.630
This brand...

00:07:17.830 --> 00:07:19.510
seems quite expensive.

00:07:21.950 --> 00:07:23.280
What do you think, Wang?

00:07:23.870 --> 00:07:25.730
It's just some lousy bird's nest.

00:07:28.270 --> 00:07:29.300
Uncle Wang, I'm heading off.

00:07:29.300 --> 00:07:29.870
Go ahead.

00:07:31.870 --> 00:07:33.510
He just had to show off, huh?

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:37.270
He's back.

00:07:42.310 --> 00:07:43.040
Dad!

00:07:43.159 --> 00:07:46.600
Xiaole made a lot of tasty food. Come eat!

00:07:47.159 --> 00:07:48.000
So delicious.

00:07:51.070 --> 00:07:51.930
I'm not hungry.

00:07:57.070 --> 00:07:57.750
But I am.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.300
How about moving this?

00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:17.190
Check.

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:22.420
There you are, Xiaole.

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:23.370
Hi, Uncle Wang.

00:08:23.510 --> 00:08:24.080
Uncle Li.

00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:26.270
Uncle Dong,

00:08:26.750 --> 00:08:27.160
I guess

00:08:27.290 --> 00:08:29.040
you must be thirsty, aren't you?

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:29.840
Have some tea.

00:08:30.660 --> 00:08:31.190
Oh right.

00:08:31.580 --> 00:08:33.150
I also brought you pastries

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:34.510
and stuff.

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:35.890
Help yourself

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.650
if you get hungry later.

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.500
What a considerate young man.

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:42.030
Yes.
He even brought pastries and water here.

00:08:48.390 --> 00:08:49.030
Come on.

00:08:49.470 --> 00:08:50.070
Have some.

00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:51.420
I don't eat sweets.

00:08:51.550 --> 00:08:52.410
Just dig in.

00:08:52.430 --> 00:08:53.670
Don't stand on ceremony.

00:08:53.670 --> 00:08:55.000
Grab a piece, Mrs. Wang.

00:08:57.550 --> 00:08:58.750
Hurry up. Make a move.

00:08:59.390 --> 00:09:00.240
I just took a pawn of yours.

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.030
You did?

00:09:02.150 --> 00:09:02.510
I...

00:09:02.630 --> 00:09:04.290
I'll take a piece of yours too!

00:09:05.510 --> 00:09:06.360
Uncle Dong,

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:09.270
I've always admired you for raising

00:09:09.300 --> 00:09:10.870
a wonderful child like Lan.

00:09:11.020 --> 00:09:12.790
Today, in the presence of these elders,

00:09:12.790 --> 00:09:13.630
I promise

00:09:13.910 --> 00:09:14.630
that from now on,

00:09:14.630 --> 00:09:15.830
I will treat Lan well.

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.550
Not many young people nowadays
can be this thoughtful

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:19.790
and caring.

00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:23.910
Okay, I got it.

00:09:24.450 --> 00:09:25.250
Just make sure

00:09:26.150 --> 00:09:27.280
you treat Lan right.

00:09:31.460 --> 00:09:32.400
It's your turn.

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:41.630
We just watched the Dream Orchestra
rehearse.

00:09:41.630 --> 00:09:42.560
Did you enjoy it?

00:09:42.630 --> 00:09:43.560
I did, of course.

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.510
Thank you so much for bringing me here.

00:09:45.510 --> 00:09:46.710
You're very welcome.

00:09:46.790 --> 00:09:48.170
I've known those musicians since school.

00:09:48.170 --> 00:09:48.670
This visit actually

00:09:48.670 --> 00:09:50.550
gave me a chance to catch up with them.

00:09:50.550 --> 00:09:51.860
It's still early now.

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:53.090
Hello, Ning.

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:54.790
I found a fantastic restaurant.

00:09:54.790 --> 00:09:55.990
Let's go there later.

00:09:57.630 --> 00:09:59.260
Eating out again?

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:00.910
But I'm a bit occupied now.

00:10:00.910 --> 00:10:02.120
I'll call you back soon.

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:02.580
Then...

00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:05.740
Do you have a date lined up?

00:10:06.100 --> 00:10:06.900
It's nothing.

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:07.730
Let's go.

00:10:07.870 --> 00:10:08.270
Okay.

00:10:11.750 --> 00:10:14.150
Their chief conductor is so professional.

00:10:14.750 --> 00:10:16.150
He's my mentor.

00:10:18.660 --> 00:10:19.870
The bar's not far away. It's right ahead.

00:10:19.870 --> 00:10:20.240
Okay.

00:10:24.630 --> 00:10:26.160
I got you some orange juice.

00:10:26.670 --> 00:10:27.270
Thank you.

00:10:30.410 --> 00:10:31.270
There's going to be

00:10:31.270 --> 00:10:32.390
a party in a few days.

00:10:32.390 --> 00:10:33.850
Will you attend it with me?

00:10:34.150 --> 00:10:36.210
Many industry leaders will be there.

00:10:36.270 --> 00:10:37.000
I believe...

00:10:37.510 --> 00:10:39.030
making more new acquaintances

00:10:39.030 --> 00:10:40.830
will benefit you in the long run,

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.790
especially when you need their help

00:10:42.790 --> 00:10:44.320
after coming back from abroad.

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:44.840
Yu,

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:46.670
you've given me so much help

00:10:46.670 --> 00:10:48.270
and always looked out for me.

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:50.230
I don't know how to thank you.

00:10:51.270 --> 00:10:52.550
Don't even mention it.

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:54.500
Sometimes

00:10:54.530 --> 00:10:55.390
when I see you,

00:10:55.670 --> 00:10:57.750
I think of when I was studying abroad.

00:10:57.870 --> 00:10:58.630
Back then,

00:10:58.870 --> 00:11:00.720
my family fell into a terrible state.

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:02.040
I had no choice but to take many odd jobs.

00:11:02.040 --> 00:11:03.100
Come to think of it,

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.990
that rough patch is finally behind me.

00:11:04.990 --> 00:11:05.630
So,

00:11:06.440 --> 00:11:07.630
I know what you must be

00:11:07.630 --> 00:11:08.230
thinking.

00:11:18.690 --> 00:11:19.160
Ning,

00:11:20.110 --> 00:11:21.240
do you know that guy?

00:11:21.510 --> 00:11:23.170
Why does he keep staring at us?

00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:29.830
Yu,

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.350
I have something to do.

00:11:31.350 --> 00:11:32.210
I need to go now.

00:11:33.110 --> 00:11:33.440
Okay.

00:11:33.470 --> 00:11:34.000
Alright.

00:11:37.830 --> 00:11:38.590
I'm leaving then.

00:11:38.590 --> 00:11:38.990
Okay.

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:39.630
Take care.

00:11:39.630 --> 00:11:39.890
Yes.

00:11:40.230 --> 00:11:40.490
Bye.

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:45.470
Ning!

00:11:46.920 --> 00:11:47.510
Ning...

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:52.930
I didn't mean to intrude, Ning.

00:11:53.230 --> 00:11:54.230
I followed you...

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:55.110
I followed you in there

00:11:55.110 --> 00:11:55.870
because I was curious.

00:11:55.870 --> 00:11:57.400
That was all there was to it.

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:59.400
I'm sorry. My apologies.

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:03.470
I only did that out of worry...

00:12:04.470 --> 00:12:05.160
Ning.

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:10.200
Ning!

00:12:11.230 --> 00:12:11.830
Chen Fan,

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:13.750
my primary goal right now is...

00:12:13.750 --> 00:12:15.280
The exchange student spot,

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:15.840
right?

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:17.840
I know that's important to you.

00:12:19.250 --> 00:12:20.350
I didn't mean to pry.

00:12:20.350 --> 00:12:22.900
I heard about it from Mengmeng
by accident.

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:24.120
I'm in need of money.

00:12:25.010 --> 00:12:26.270
I know it sounds tacky,

00:12:26.350 --> 00:12:27.440
but this is what I need,

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:28.440
for studying abroad,

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:29.830
my dreams, and my family.

00:12:29.830 --> 00:12:30.750
I can help you with...

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:31.960
I know you can.

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:33.710
But I don't want your money.

00:12:33.710 --> 00:12:34.710
I don't want your pity.

00:12:34.710 --> 00:12:36.110
I reject to depend on anyone,

00:12:36.110 --> 00:12:37.470
be it you or my parents.

00:12:37.870 --> 00:12:40.440
I'm determined to realize my dreams
with my own efforts.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:41.440
If you're looking

00:12:41.590 --> 00:12:43.720
for a girlfriend who's always around,

00:12:44.510 --> 00:12:45.350
I can't be that girl.

00:12:45.350 --> 00:12:46.990
I'm not showing you pity.

00:12:47.830 --> 00:12:49.870
I'm supportive of you chasing your dreams.

00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:51.530
I want to study abroad as well.

00:12:51.590 --> 00:12:54.320
I just want to be with you,
no matter where you are.

00:12:56.710 --> 00:12:57.510
Chen Fan,

00:12:58.440 --> 00:13:00.770
how does being with me solve any problems?

00:13:01.470 --> 00:13:02.670
I'm off for practice.

00:13:03.710 --> 00:13:04.710
Luo Ningzi,

00:13:05.110 --> 00:13:06.440
all of this is weird!

00:13:06.990 --> 00:13:09.190
I'm your boyfriend, yet I know nothing.

00:13:09.510 --> 00:13:11.110
I spend every day waiting for you
like a fool.

00:13:11.110 --> 00:13:12.970
We've never been on a proper date.

00:13:13.830 --> 00:13:15.830
I don't even know where your home is!

00:13:52.230 --> 00:13:52.830
Yi Lan.

00:13:57.080 --> 00:13:57.680
Did you...

00:13:57.830 --> 00:13:59.110
prepare all these?

00:14:00.400 --> 00:14:02.920
Do you know
how many paper cranes there are?

00:14:06.230 --> 00:14:07.040
No.

00:14:08.120 --> 00:14:09.850
Three hundred and sixty-four,

00:14:09.990 --> 00:14:10.990
only one short

00:14:12.080 --> 00:14:13.940
of three hundred and sixty-five.

00:14:21.800 --> 00:14:23.000
Unfold it and read it.

00:14:29.090 --> 00:14:30.690
Isn't it what I wrote before?

00:14:31.510 --> 00:14:33.930
[Please let me have a romance]

00:14:36.110 --> 00:14:36.770
Will you...

00:14:40.700 --> 00:14:41.580
let me help you

00:14:42.670 --> 00:14:45.700
fulfill the wish
written on this piece of paper?

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:51.990
Yes.

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:55.690
Then, what am I to you

00:14:56.080 --> 00:14:56.350
now?

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:00.960
My...

00:15:01.110 --> 00:15:01.830
boyfriend.

00:15:02.590 --> 00:15:03.350
And

00:15:03.350 --> 00:15:04.190
you're

00:15:04.220 --> 00:15:05.080
my girlfriend.

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:11.710
Well,

00:15:12.080 --> 00:15:13.740
you kissed me the other day...

00:15:13.990 --> 00:15:16.420
I only intended to kiss your cheek,

00:15:16.510 --> 00:15:17.960
but you turned your face around.

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:19.490
You just took my first kiss.

00:15:21.590 --> 00:15:23.050
T-That one doesn't count.

00:15:23.470 --> 00:15:24.230
The real one

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:26.230
will

00:15:26.350 --> 00:15:26.750
happen

00:15:26.870 --> 00:15:27.450
today.

00:15:36.320 --> 00:15:36.680
Lan!

00:15:36.710 --> 00:15:37.630
Lan, i-i-it's time

00:15:37.630 --> 00:15:38.230
to go home.

00:15:38.230 --> 00:15:38.630
U-Uncle...

00:15:38.630 --> 00:15:38.960
Dad!

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:39.620
Uncle Dong.

00:15:40.140 --> 00:15:41.870
Xiaole, you should go home too.

00:15:42.350 --> 00:15:42.710
Dad,

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:44.080
Xiaole

00:15:44.470 --> 00:15:45.440
is my boyfriend now.

00:15:45.440 --> 00:15:47.130
You must not be mean to him again.

00:15:47.130 --> 00:15:47.400
I...

00:15:48.130 --> 00:15:48.470
Wait.

00:15:48.710 --> 00:15:50.390
W-When have I ever been mean to him?

00:15:50.390 --> 00:15:51.350
Let's go home.

00:15:51.630 --> 00:15:52.710
Give them some space.

00:15:52.710 --> 00:15:53.200
No.

00:15:53.470 --> 00:15:54.990
It's late.
The residents will be disturbed.

00:15:54.990 --> 00:15:56.250
You can talk tomorrow.

00:15:56.350 --> 00:15:56.740
Lan,

00:15:56.890 --> 00:15:57.690
let's go home.

00:15:57.710 --> 00:15:58.110
Okay.

00:15:58.440 --> 00:15:59.080
Let's go.

00:15:59.630 --> 00:16:00.530
Just go.

00:16:01.470 --> 00:16:02.750
Go to bed early, Uncle Dong!

00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:04.080
I won't be able to sleep!

00:16:06.110 --> 00:16:07.910
Don't forget our date tomorrow.

00:16:08.350 --> 00:16:08.750
Well,

00:16:08.830 --> 00:16:09.830
I'm leaving then.

00:16:10.350 --> 00:16:11.610
Aren't you going home?

00:16:13.350 --> 00:16:15.410
Not until I put away the paper cranes.

00:16:15.510 --> 00:16:16.470
I'll go then.

00:16:16.750 --> 00:16:17.320
Bye.

00:16:22.800 --> 00:16:23.660
I'll beat that.

00:16:24.230 --> 00:16:24.590
A two.

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:26.350
Seriously,

00:16:26.350 --> 00:16:28.610
your daughter Lan has great taste in men.

00:16:28.830 --> 00:16:29.440
That's for sure.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:30.200
In fact,

00:16:30.350 --> 00:16:32.350
Wang has long had his eyes on Xiaole.

00:16:32.510 --> 00:16:33.440
His daughter,

00:16:33.590 --> 00:16:34.710
a broadcasting major,

00:16:34.710 --> 00:16:35.710
is really pretty.

00:16:35.960 --> 00:16:36.750
Unexpectedly,

00:16:36.750 --> 00:16:38.830
your daughter Lan snatched Xiaole away.

00:16:38.830 --> 00:16:40.580
It's not fair to say that, is it?

00:16:40.710 --> 00:16:41.680
Do you mean

00:16:42.110 --> 00:16:43.970
Lan is not good enough for Xiaole?

00:16:44.560 --> 00:16:46.760
He excels in academics, and that's all.

00:16:47.200 --> 00:16:48.350
Listen to yourself.

00:16:48.590 --> 00:16:49.190
You should

00:16:49.230 --> 00:16:50.590
really change your attitude

00:16:50.590 --> 00:16:51.520
towards Xiaole.

00:16:54.440 --> 00:16:56.080
My daughter Lan is an excellent kid too,

00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:56.680
isn't she?

00:16:56.990 --> 00:16:58.710
She'll be a great artist in the future.

00:16:58.710 --> 00:16:59.840
Xiaole actually...

00:16:59.990 --> 00:17:01.350
owes me respect.

00:17:01.830 --> 00:17:02.290
Come on.

00:17:02.590 --> 00:17:03.450
Try to top this.

00:17:03.630 --> 00:17:04.730
Okay, fine.

00:17:05.839 --> 00:17:06.310
A bomb!

00:17:07.790 --> 00:17:09.990
Why target me? Only he's the "landlord"!

00:17:09.990 --> 00:17:11.640
Because I want to lay down more cards.

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:12.839
Why should I wait for you?

00:17:12.839 --> 00:17:14.710
Do you even know how to play cards?
You've become...

00:17:14.710 --> 00:17:15.640
I'm done with it!

00:17:16.990 --> 00:17:18.550
Dong, do you have to be like this?

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:20.030
We're only having a random chat.

00:17:20.030 --> 00:17:21.230
Why lose your temper?

00:17:21.230 --> 00:17:22.069
What's all this for?

00:17:22.069 --> 00:17:24.470
There are boundaries even in chats, right?

00:17:24.990 --> 00:17:25.790
Leave my home!

00:17:27.470 --> 00:17:28.200
Fine, I quit.

00:17:28.200 --> 00:17:28.660
Oh, you.

00:17:28.680 --> 00:17:29.610
The game's over.

00:17:29.880 --> 00:17:30.510
Look at him,

00:17:30.510 --> 00:17:31.510
so hot tempered.

00:17:31.990 --> 00:17:33.650
Where are you going? That way!

00:17:36.160 --> 00:17:36.550
Let's go.

00:17:36.550 --> 00:17:38.480
H-H-He got so worked up over a game.

00:17:38.680 --> 00:17:41.990
You still don't know where the door is,
though you've been here many times.

00:17:41.990 --> 00:17:42.510
Uncle Li.

00:17:42.510 --> 00:17:43.440
Hello, Xiaole.

00:17:43.550 --> 00:17:44.880
You're here too, Uncle Wang.

00:17:44.880 --> 00:17:45.270
Take care.

00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:45.710
Okay.

00:17:48.920 --> 00:17:49.580
Uncle Dong,

00:17:49.990 --> 00:17:51.270
you were playing cards?

00:17:51.270 --> 00:17:51.870
Oh, right.

00:17:56.160 --> 00:17:56.620
What...

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:59.550
do you think of Wang's daughter?

00:18:00.310 --> 00:18:00.970
Uncle Dong,

00:18:01.030 --> 00:18:02.490
I'm not familiar with her.

00:18:04.740 --> 00:18:05.540
Not familiar?

00:18:06.230 --> 00:18:06.960
That's good.

00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:08.160
There you are.

00:18:08.270 --> 00:18:08.990
Lan.

00:18:15.880 --> 00:18:16.510
Where...

00:18:17.470 --> 00:18:18.750
are you taking Lan?

00:18:19.470 --> 00:18:19.790
W-We

00:18:19.990 --> 00:18:22.420
are only going for a walk in the park.

00:18:23.920 --> 00:18:24.880
The park, huh?

00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:27.550
Xuan!

00:18:28.230 --> 00:18:28.710
D-Don't

00:18:28.770 --> 00:18:30.170
you want to go to the park?

00:18:30.470 --> 00:18:31.920
I have to do my homework now.

00:18:31.920 --> 00:18:32.780
What homework?

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:34.160
Forget it. Go play in the park!

00:18:34.160 --> 00:18:34.560
Hurry.

00:18:37.750 --> 00:18:38.550
Come here.

00:18:39.640 --> 00:18:40.640
Put on your shoes.

00:18:41.710 --> 00:18:42.750
Listen up.

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:46.820
Keep an eye on your sister for Dad.

00:18:46.990 --> 00:18:48.200
Have her come home early.

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:49.470
I'll buy you a new toy then.

00:18:49.470 --> 00:18:51.360
And I request my favorite one.

00:18:51.510 --> 00:18:52.270
Consider it done.

00:18:52.270 --> 00:18:52.870
Off you go.

00:18:53.510 --> 00:18:54.400
Come here, Xuan.

00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:54.860
Come on.

00:18:55.640 --> 00:18:57.030
Uncle Dong, rest assured.
I'll take good care of him.

00:18:57.030 --> 00:18:57.470
Okay.

00:19:00.510 --> 00:19:01.040
Let's go.

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:02.030
Bye, Dad.

00:19:02.030 --> 00:19:02.470
Bye.

00:19:02.470 --> 00:19:03.600
We're leaving then.

00:19:05.990 --> 00:19:07.790
Let's go to the park.

00:19:08.600 --> 00:19:09.750
Off to the park!

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:11.510
I guess...

00:19:11.510 --> 00:19:12.810
my dad didn't mean any harm.

00:19:12.810 --> 00:19:14.410
Hope you don't take offense.

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:16.980
Is Uncle Dong...

00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:18.360
still mad about

00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:21.640
what happened at my place earlier?

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:22.880
Well...

00:19:23.510 --> 00:19:27.070
I don't think so. Otherwise,
he wouldn't have let me go out with you.

00:19:27.070 --> 00:19:28.070
That makes sense.

00:19:29.750 --> 00:19:30.550
I'm wondering...

00:19:30.550 --> 00:19:32.410
what couples usually do on a date.

00:19:33.230 --> 00:19:36.270
They hold hands first,
as it is seen on TV.

00:19:41.880 --> 00:19:42.590
What's up?

00:19:43.310 --> 00:19:44.240
Anything wrong?

00:19:44.710 --> 00:19:46.880
Sister, it's like my skin's on fire.

00:19:46.990 --> 00:19:48.030
I want to go home.

00:19:48.030 --> 00:19:49.830
Didn't we just come out?

00:19:50.400 --> 00:19:51.800
It's too early to go home.

00:19:52.270 --> 00:19:55.070
But I'm really burning up and starving.

00:19:55.270 --> 00:19:57.070
I want to go home.

00:19:57.440 --> 00:19:57.860
Look.

00:19:57.990 --> 00:19:59.680
My arms are getting tanned.

00:19:59.680 --> 00:20:00.960
But you were born this shade.

00:20:00.960 --> 00:20:02.650
Sister!

00:20:06.230 --> 00:20:06.990
Xuan.

00:20:08.440 --> 00:20:10.160
When we get to the convenience store,

00:20:10.160 --> 00:20:11.350
how about I buy you

00:20:11.370 --> 00:20:13.300
something to eat, drink, and play?

00:20:15.230 --> 00:20:16.990
I'm not in the mood for food.

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:19.290
My belly hurts.

00:20:19.470 --> 00:20:21.470
I want to go home.

00:20:21.470 --> 00:20:23.010
Your belly hurts?

00:20:23.160 --> 00:20:23.880
Let me see.

00:20:30.070 --> 00:20:30.680
Xuan,

00:20:31.030 --> 00:20:32.760
isn't your birthday coming up?

00:20:33.070 --> 00:20:34.040
Why don't I...

00:20:34.230 --> 00:20:35.920
buy you a birthday present?

00:20:35.990 --> 00:20:36.750
You can pick

00:20:37.030 --> 00:20:37.990
whatever you want,

00:20:37.990 --> 00:20:38.440
okay?

00:20:38.790 --> 00:20:39.200
Okay!

00:20:39.920 --> 00:20:40.440
Well,

00:20:40.710 --> 00:20:41.680
after that,

00:20:43.270 --> 00:20:44.990
tell me what your dad said

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:45.990
to you,

00:20:46.170 --> 00:20:46.700
will you?

00:20:46.710 --> 00:20:47.550
No problem.

00:20:48.230 --> 00:20:49.630
Let's make a pinky swear.

00:20:50.710 --> 00:20:51.510
Seal the deal.

00:20:52.230 --> 00:20:53.090
Come on, kiddo.

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:54.100
Have a bite.

00:20:55.160 --> 00:20:55.960
Is it good?

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:57.880
Xuan!

00:20:59.200 --> 00:20:59.680
Xuan?

00:21:03.920 --> 00:21:05.070
Make a report now.

00:21:06.680 --> 00:21:10.620
All Xiaole and Sister did was talk.

00:21:10.750 --> 00:21:14.110
I said my belly hurt,
so they brought me home.

00:21:14.130 --> 00:21:14.790
Well done.

00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:15.890
From now on,

00:21:16.710 --> 00:21:18.380
keep watch on them for Dad.

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:19.200
Sure.

00:21:21.270 --> 00:21:22.130
Your pocket...

00:21:37.230 --> 00:21:37.720
Ning,

00:21:38.070 --> 00:21:39.130
are you still busy?

00:21:39.210 --> 00:21:40.340
Let's eat together.

00:21:40.410 --> 00:21:42.070
I'll wait for you downstairs.

00:21:44.440 --> 00:21:45.710
Let it be my treat today.

00:21:45.710 --> 00:21:47.630
I was a bit harsh on you last time.

00:21:47.790 --> 00:21:48.270
Sorry.

00:21:49.070 --> 00:21:51.130
I'll get my stuff and be with you soon.

00:21:51.790 --> 00:21:52.400
Ning,

00:21:52.880 --> 00:21:54.200
I transferred the pay for the gig to you.

00:21:54.200 --> 00:21:54.990
Collect it in time.

00:21:54.990 --> 00:21:55.710
Thanks, Yu.

00:21:56.510 --> 00:21:57.160
Oh, right.

00:21:57.470 --> 00:21:58.200
Here is...

00:21:58.310 --> 00:21:59.110
a gift for you.

00:21:59.990 --> 00:22:00.470
This...

00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:03.090
Don't get me wrong.

00:22:03.510 --> 00:22:05.070
That party's coming up, right?

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:07.270
I've noticed that you always carry
a cello case around.

00:22:07.270 --> 00:22:08.790
I bet you need a purse.

00:22:09.030 --> 00:22:10.920
You'll attend the party as my plus-one.

00:22:10.920 --> 00:22:13.520
Just do me a favor
and bring this purse with you.

00:22:15.510 --> 00:22:16.230
Take it.

00:22:17.550 --> 00:22:18.310
Thank you.

00:22:21.230 --> 00:22:22.290
About the young man

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:24.690
we met in the bar previously...

00:22:24.990 --> 00:22:26.230
Don't worry about that.

00:22:26.230 --> 00:22:27.430
I've taken care of it.

00:22:27.750 --> 00:22:29.010
He was Chen Fan, right?

00:22:30.790 --> 00:22:32.140
How did you...

00:22:32.510 --> 00:22:34.440
Actually, this gig you just did...

00:22:37.710 --> 00:22:38.440
Yu.

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:40.880
Actually,

00:22:41.550 --> 00:22:42.990
Chen Fan specifically asked me

00:22:42.990 --> 00:22:44.550
to choose you for this gig.

00:22:46.710 --> 00:22:48.710
He told me to keep it secret from you.

00:22:49.990 --> 00:22:50.640
Oh, right.

00:22:53.360 --> 00:22:53.960
And this.

00:22:54.270 --> 00:22:56.200
He insisted that I keep it,
though I tried to refuse.

00:22:56.200 --> 00:22:57.990
A talented musician as you are
doesn't need such help.

00:22:57.990 --> 00:22:58.720
How about...

00:22:58.790 --> 00:23:00.050
you return this to him?

00:23:01.710 --> 00:23:02.440
Just keep it,

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:03.900
since he gave it to you.

00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:07.010
Well...

00:23:07.230 --> 00:23:08.290
I'll take off then.

00:23:12.990 --> 00:23:13.550
Bye.

00:23:32.710 --> 00:23:33.230
Ning.

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:37.440
Sit down.

00:23:41.750 --> 00:23:43.410
Listen, I've really found...

00:23:43.610 --> 00:23:45.470
a fantastic restaurant.

00:23:46.960 --> 00:23:47.490
Chen Fan,

00:23:47.990 --> 00:23:48.990
tell me the truth.

00:23:49.470 --> 00:23:50.270
Did I get a spot

00:23:50.470 --> 00:23:51.930
in this gig because of you?

00:23:57.640 --> 00:23:59.030
Yes or no?

00:24:04.470 --> 00:24:05.230
I was just...

00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:07.930
trying to lighten your burden.

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:13.960
Let me ask you.

00:24:14.710 --> 00:24:16.570
What exactly do you like about me?

00:24:17.470 --> 00:24:18.230
Everything.

00:24:18.790 --> 00:24:20.310
I like everything about you.

00:24:20.310 --> 00:24:21.510
That's not an answer.

00:24:21.640 --> 00:24:22.990
There has to be a reason
for liking someone.

00:24:22.990 --> 00:24:24.790
Why does there have to be a reason

00:24:24.990 --> 00:24:25.990
for liking someone?

00:24:25.990 --> 00:24:26.990
It's how it works.

00:24:27.230 --> 00:24:30.290
Motives and plans are needed
before one does anything.

00:24:30.510 --> 00:24:32.170
You can't just act on impulse.

00:24:33.880 --> 00:24:36.210
How are you so sure
that I don't have a plan?

00:24:37.470 --> 00:24:37.990
Fine.

00:24:38.470 --> 00:24:39.330
You have a plan.

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:40.580
Then tell me

00:24:40.960 --> 00:24:41.960
what your plan is.

00:24:42.230 --> 00:24:42.710
I...

00:24:47.160 --> 00:24:48.160
So typical of you.

00:24:48.440 --> 00:24:49.710
You never think before you act,

00:24:49.710 --> 00:24:51.710
knowing that your family
will always have your back.

00:24:51.710 --> 00:24:54.030
You're just a loser
relying on your family,

00:24:54.030 --> 00:24:55.310
always trying to shape my life

00:24:55.310 --> 00:24:56.270
the way you like.

00:24:56.400 --> 00:24:58.230
Have you ever considered what I want?

00:24:58.230 --> 00:25:00.230
I just hope you can be happy.

00:25:00.230 --> 00:25:00.990
Happy?

00:25:10.070 --> 00:25:11.200
How to achieve that?

00:25:11.790 --> 00:25:13.190
With your family's help?

00:25:18.230 --> 00:25:19.470
I hate those relying on their families.